♪ Just a little bit,
just a little bit ♪

1:40:49.299 --> 1:40:51.760
♪ Just a little bit over ♪

1:40:52.261 --> 1:40:55.597
♪ Just a little bit,
just a little bit ♪

1:40:55.681 --> 1:40:59.434
♪ Just a little bit over again♪

1:41:07.734 --> 1:41:08.694
Oh.

1:41:09.486 --> 1:41:10.654
Shit.

1:41:13.448 --> 1:41:15.117
Watch the merchandise.

1:41:17.160 --> 1:41:18.287
Oh.

1:41:20.622 --> 1:41:21.748
My goodness.

1:41:23.959 --> 1:41:26.378
In the end, Peter got it wrong.

1:41:26.753 --> 1:41:28.672
It's living, not dying,

1:41:28.755 --> 1:41:30.549
that's the awfully
big adventure.

1:41:31.925 --> 1:41:34.595
Living requires
more imagination.

1:41:36.263 --> 1:41:37.264
Hey.

1:41:38.640 --> 1:41:42.019
I was just looking for that
book, Bunny's Blue, remember?

1:41:42.269 --> 1:41:43.187
Yes?

1:41:43.312 --> 1:41:45.898
I think I'm going to have
to rework the ending.

